'''Nyu Yurk''' (s [[Tanglizt|tnglizt]]: -{New York}-)— ttussan bahra s ddu yism n '''Tamdint n Nyu Yurk''' (s [[Tanglizt|tnglizt]]: -{New York City}-) fad ad yili umzaray d tsga n [[Tasga n Nyu Yurk|Nyu Yurk]]— nttat ad igan tamdint lli akkʷ ittuzdaɣn ɣ [[Iwankn Munnin n Marikan|Iwankn Munnin]], d nttat ad akkʷ imqqurn ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Nyu Yurk|Nyu Yurk]] ula ḥtta ɣ [[Iwankn Munnin n Marikan|Iwankn Munnin]], tg ula tamdint nna iṭṭafn yiḍiṣ lli akkʷ ixatrn ɣ yigran n tsbbabt d iqaṛiḍn, asnɣms d tẓuṛi d tmlsiwin, tussna d ttiknulujya, asslmd d tmallayt.

Tga tamdint n Nyu Yurk yat zɣ wammasn n tsbbabt d iqaṛiḍn bahra istawhmman ɣ umaḍal, nttat ad igan tamaẓunt tadmsant n [[Iwankn Munnin n Marikan|Iwankn Munnin]] acku ɣinn a ɣ munn timssurin d id bank imaḍlann, yili gis ula wammas n [[Timtta Imunn]].
